message:
Blog post from the reCAPTCHA product manager at Google commenting on the ICLR 2014 paper by the Google StreetView and Brain folks.
During his ICLR talk, Julian Ibarz said their ConvNet-based system can recognize Google's CAPTCHAs with 99.8% accuracy ("better than humans" according to Julian).
